headline: A Look At ONEOK’s (OKE) Valuation After Its Recent Share Price Rally
summary: Why ONEOK Is On Investors’ Radar Right Now ONEOK (OKE) has drawn fresh attention after recent share price moves, with the stock up about 12% over the past month and roughly 24% in the past 3 months, prompting investors to reassess its current valuation. See our latest analysis for ONEOK. Looking beyond the recent rally, ONEOK’s 30 day share price return of 11.96% and 90 day share price return of 24.35% sit alongside a 5 year total shareholder return of 161.56%.
